         <abstract id="aspace_808d0ed9e89529e62d961a8047a4ed0d">Correspondence and printed material document the work of the Evangelical and Reformed Church China mission. George and Grace Snyder were American missionaries in Yuanling, Hunan Province, China, serving under the Evangelical and Reformed Church from 1920 to 1950.</abstract>
